-- Title: "What's your office mandate?"                                         
-- Slider for percentage (25%–100%, step 5%).                                   
-- Display: "X% of working days".                                               
-- Default: 50%.                                                                
-- Working days row: label "Which days do you work?" + a row of 7 toggleable day
chips (M T W T F S S). Mon–Fri selected by default. At least one day must remain
selected. Sat/Sun chips are visually de-emphasised but still tappable.          
-                                                                               
-**Step 2 — Period Selection:**                                                 
-- Title: "How is your mandate measured?"                                       
-- 4 radio options: Weekly / Monthly / Quarterly / Rolling 4 weeks.             
                                           
